text:
Ah, Harukic-han!
You waited for me.

I made you wait for so long, didn't I?
The interview ended up being quite lengthy...

Nah, it's okay~
I wanted to go home together today, so I waited.

Oh, could it be...
Do you want to go eat something?

That sounds good too~ But, you know, today,
my makeup and hairstyle were done so nicely, right?
It makes me want to go out on the town~!

Hehe, I'll hurry up and get ready,
so wait a moment, okay?
